text: The Ganja-Gazakh Economic Region is one of ten economic regions in Azerbaijan. It is in the western part of the country. It consists of Agstafa, Dashkesen, Gadabay, Goranboy, Goygol, Gazakh, Samukh, Shamkir, Tovuz administrative districts and cities such as Ganja and Naftalan. ==Related pages== *Economic regions of Azerbaijan
title: Ganja-Gazakh Economic Region
